Package: numspell
Type: Package
Title: Spell Numbers into Words (French and English)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ousmane", "Ouedraogo", email = "oousmane@proton.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Convert integers and decimals into words with correct orthography in French and English. Supports negatives, large magnitudes, and currency-like formatting with units and subunits.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.6)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Language: en
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
